    <acqinfo encodinganalog="541">
      <p>Collection 2140 was received from the Museum of the Rockies in 1985 with other business
        paper collections and had no individual accession number. In 1970, Marjorie Durand of
        Phillipsburg, Montana donated accession 886, a group of Granite Mountain Mining Company
        papers which has been combined with the 2140 collection. Additional materials, arranged as
        folders 6-12 in Box 2, were donated by Darlene Mills of Lolo, Montana on March 16, 2015.</p>
    </acqinfo>
